parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch handle can cause the door to remain unlatched, leading to potential accidents or injuries when the door suddenly opens while the vehicle is in motion.
symptoms: The door latch handle stays up when opened
the door will not latch when closed
the window needs to be rolled down to push the handle down to latch the door.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hood latch striker can cause the hood to fly open while driving, obstructing the driver's visibility and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: the hood flies up while driving
the windshield is damaged or broken
the hood needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can lead to inadequate restraint, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle is difficult to buckle
the seat belt does not restrain the driver or passenger
the seat belt detaches from the door during an accident

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption and engine oil leaks can cause engine damage, lead to costly repairs, and pose a safety risk due to reduced visibility from smoke emitted from the vehicle.
symptoms: excessive smoke coming out of the vehicle

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cylinder head/exhaust valve failure can cause engine damage, lead to costly repairs, and pose a safety risk due to potential engine stalling or failure while driving.
